  <main style="padding: 20px; max-width: 800px; margin: auto; line-height: 1.6;">
    <section>
      <h2>1. Returns & Refunds</h2>
      <p>
        At TickOrder, we strive to ensure you are satisfied with your purchase. If you are not completely happy with an item, you may request a refund or exchange under the following conditions:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Items must be returned within <strong>7 days</strong> of delivery.</li>
        <li>Products must be unused, in the original packaging, and in the same condition as received.</li>
        <li>Some items, such as perishable goods or personalized products, may not be eligible for a refund. This will be clearly indicated on the product page.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>2. How to Request a Refund</h2>
      <p>
        To request a refund, please contact us via email at <strong>tickorderstore@gmail.com</strong> or call <strong>0766506107</strong> with your order number and reason for the return. We will guide you through the return process.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>3. Refund Process</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Once we receive the returned item and confirm it meets our refund conditions, we will process your refund within <strong>5 business days</strong>.</li>
        <li>Refunds will be made via the same payment method used for the original purchase.</li>
        <li>Shipping fees are non-refundable, unless the return is due to a defect or error on our side.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>4. Exchanges</h2>
      <p>
        If you prefer an exchange, please contact us with the item details. Exchanges are subject to product availability.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>5. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        For any questions regarding refunds or returns, reach out via <strong>tickorderstore@gmail.com</strong> or call <strong>0766506107</strong>.
      </p>
    </section>
